text: Mavlyutovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Bakayevsky Selsoviet, Kushnarenkovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 38 as of 2010. There is 1 streets. == Geography == It is located 21 km from Kushnarenkovo, 3 km from Bakayevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kushnarenkovsky District
title: Mavlyutovo
